name: BIMxHTML
description: Generate dynamic HTML web pages using live data from a Revit model.
contents: Data Set - Quantities of Family Types - Creates a list of family types for a category with wublists containing the family type name and quantity., Generate Web Page - Google Bar Chart - Generate HTML code for a web page to display a bar chart using Google Charts., Generate Web Page - Google Pie Chart - Generates the HTML code for a web page that displays a responsive Google Pie Chart., Generate Web Page - Creates a static web page from a string formatted as HTML.
